            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Very good School. In case you want overall development of your child this is the right school for you. They have good command over every field like Academics , sports , NCC and other activities. Just attended republic day celebration at school NCC cadets trained by NCC incharge  performed extreamly amazing. Before this we attended theatre festival at taal katora stadium delhi, that was an awsome show full of extraordinary performances of kids. They have MUN functions , Inter-ryan tournaments and many more. Even students of grade one and two are groomed well so they can perform on stage. They have also produced many sports persons at national level in different games. Recently one ex student nitin pandey (Bhondsi) got selected as an army officer.",
